OL,3,CChurch walls and gravestones
OL,4,Cvandalised at Grade II listed church
OL,6,FAn attack on a grade II listed church
OL,7,Fin Lancashire by vandals, which
OL,8,Fdamaged walls and 40 gravestones is
OL,9,Fbeing treated as a hate crime.
OL,11,FThe vandalism at St James Church in
OL,12,FMoss Side, near Leyland was discovered
OL,13,Fjust after 9:30am on Good Friday.
OL,14,FPolice are now investigating.
OL,16,FThe Revd Marc A.M. Wolverson, the
OL,17,Fchurch's vicar told ITV Granada: "It
OL,18,Fmade me feel very sad on one level.
