OL,6,F"I was shocked and disappointed when I
OL,7,Fwas made aware of it. A local
OL,8,Fneighbour came and told me. I was
OL,9,Freally devastated."
OL,11,FThe church which has never been
OL,12,Ftargeted before was built in 1854.
OL,14,FAccording to records held by
OL,15,FLancashire County Council, it's
OL,16,Ffoundation stone was laid by Miss
OL,17,FSusan Ffarington, with the church
OL,18,Fbuilt with money donated by her mother
OL,19,Fas a memorial to her late husband,
OL,20,FJames Nowell Ffarington, the squire of
OL,21,FLeyland.
