OL,6,F"Obviously, the couple were advised
OL,7,Fabout what had happened and we're
OL,8,Ftrying to make provisions to mask some
OL,9,Fof the graffiti, so that they can go
OL,10,Fahead with their wedding pictures and
OL,11,Fthings like that.
OL,13,F"And we're doing our best to soldier
OL,14,Fon and continue and celebrate what is
OL,15,Fthe most important holy week of the
OL,16,FChristian year."
