OL,6,FDet Sgt Lee Jamieson, of Lancashire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "This is a disgraceful
OL,8,Fact of vandalism which shows a
OL,9,Fcomplete lack of respect and which has
OL,10,Fleft the church and its parishioners
OL,11,Funderstandably extremely upset,
OL,12,Fespecially given the time of year.
OL,14,F"We are taking this matter incredibly
OL,15,Fseriously and this is being treated as
OL,16,Fa hate crime.
OL,18,F"We do not tolerate hate of any form,
OL,19,Fand we will do everything in our power
OL,20,Fto identify the offenders and take the
OL,21,Fappropriate action.
